<h1>Disclaimer </h1>

<hr>

<h3 align="left">Dear friends! The &quot;Virtual Guide to Belarus&quot; is a volunteer
non-profit non-governmental collaboration started in November 1994 among <a href="Belarusians.html">a group of
Belarusian scientists</a> working around the
World. Our
goal is to bring you knowledge of our beautiful homeland in a simple and friendly way.
This site is <b>not</b> an official page. It has nothing to do with the
Belarusian
government or any other organizations. These pages state personal points of view of <a href="Belarusians.html">the authors</a> only. We are striving to provide you with the most
reliable information to the best of our knowledge. And yet Virtual Guide to Belarus holds
no responsibility for any losses or damages that occurred to you based on provided here
information. </h3>

